rn true,\n                   Some(Some(n)) => n.notified().await,\n               }\n           }\n       }\n       ```\n   \n   - **`src/fs/icache/mod.rs`** (modified — module wiring)\n     - Added `async_cache` module and `AsyncICache` re-export\n     - Current state:\n       ```rust\n       #[cfg_attr(not(test), expect(dead_code))]\n       pub mod async_cache;\n       pub mod bridge;\n       mod cache;\n       mod inode_factory;\n       \n       #[expect(unused_imports)]\n       pub use async_cache::AsyncICache;\n       pub use cache::ICache;\n       pub use inode_factory::InodeFactory;\n       \n       pub trait IcbLike {\n           fn new_root(path: std::path::PathBuf) -> Self;\n           fn rc(&self) -> u64;\n           fn rc_mut(&mut self) -> &mut u64;\n       }\n       ```\n\n   - **`src/fs/icache/cache.rs`** (read-only — sync reference)\n     - The sync `ICache<I: IcbLike>` using `HashMap<Inode, I>` — the template for the async version\n   \n   - **`src/fs/trait.rs`** (read-only — type definitions)\n     - `pub type Inode = u64; pub type FileHandle = u64;`\n     - `#[async_trait] pub trait Fs` with async methods: `lookup`, `getattr`, `readdir`, `open`, `read`, `release`, `forget`, `statfs`\n   \n   - **`src/fs/local.rs`** (read via explore — IcbLike impl)\n     - `InodeControlBlock { rc, path, children }` implementing `IcbLike`\n   \n   - **`src/fs/mescloud/icache.rs`** (read via explore — IcbLike impl)\n     - `InodeControlBlock { parent, rc, path, children, attr }` implementing `IcbLike`\n     - `MescloudICache` wrapping `ICache<InodeControlBlock>` with inode factory\n   \n   - **`src/fs/icache/bridge.rs`** (read via explore)\n     - `HashMapBridge` for inode/filehandle translation between stacked FS layers using `bimap::BiMap`\n   \n   - **`Cargo.toml`** (read — dependencies and lint config)\n     - Edition 2024, `scc = \"3.4.16\"` (resolves to 3.5.6), `tokio` full features, `async-trait = \"0.1.89\"`\n     - Strict clippy: pedantic/nursery/cargo warn,